headline: Starbucks (NasdaqGS:SBUX) Expands To Premier Metro Location In Ashburn's Loudoun Station
summary: Comstock Holding Companies Inc.'s announcement of a new Starbucks location in Loudoun Station underscores its commitment to community growth, but this expansion hasn't seemingly impacted Starbucks (NasdaqGS:SBUX) shares, which saw a 4% decline last week. This price movement bucks the overall flat market trend observed over the same period. While the broader market remains up by 6% over the past year, Starbucks's recent decline might not be closely tied to Comstock’s latest expansion news,...
